Sentencas: In the present paper, material research dealing with electrolyte, anode, cathode, interconnect and sealant for planar solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) stack has been reported.
Titulo: Material research for planar SOFC stack

Sentencas: Depending on the materials research, a two-cell stack and a 10-cell stack with cell size of 40x40 mm(2) were established and tested.
Titulo: Material research for planar SOFC stack

Sentencas: The 10-cell stack at 1000 degreesC showed a power output of about 10 W and a power density of about 110 mW/cm(2).
